splash_description: Know others, know yourself to win
onboarding_title_1:
Grand ‘Level’ for the name
that is important to me
onboarding_title_2:
Immediately tag the other
person’s memorable points.
onboarding_title_3:
It's fun and easy to decide the face of the
other person you see.
onboarding_title_4:
Zippy doesn't know who you are
or who the other person is.
onboarding_description_1:
The more important it is, the more often you see it,
 and the sooner you see it, the higher the level.
onboarding_description_2:
You can easily record all the characteristics
of the other person and easily find them by tag.
onboarding_description_3:
My honest feelings about the other person
are probably all in here, right?
onboarding_description_4:
Only your email and the other person's phone number
are completely encrypted and managed.

We don't take your name, 
the other person's name, or anything else.
onboarding_description_5:
I don't know who it is, but the honest feelings about
me from
people who have my number
Please check the ziggy report.
app_permission_settings_title:
Please allow access
to use the app
app_permission_settings_description:
If you do not agree to access your contact information, you will not be
able to use the service properly. You can set whether to allow the
remaining optional consent permission items in your phone settings.
app_permission_settings_description_cont:
Import the contact information of your friends that you want to
manage. Your device's contact information is encrypted and securely
transmitted to zippy servers and is only used to identify recorded.
app_permission_settings_description_noti: Use it to receive reminders to help you manage your network.
app_permission_settings_description_mess: Use it to send messages to friends.
app_permission_settings_description_phot: Store reputation information about myself as an image.
